### 1. *Functional Requirements*

- ***Content Management***
    - **Admin Panel** for **Content Creation & Management from where blogs will be posted on the website adding title , content , selecting category / sub category , adding seo details**
    - **Blog Posting**
    - **Content Categorization**
    
    | main category  | sub category  |
    | --- | --- |
    | Games | PS5, XBOX , Nintendo , PC  |
    | Entertainment | Movies , Series , Comics  |
    | Mobiles  | Smartphone , Accessories  |
    | tech | Tech Deals , News  |
    | Stocks  |  |
    - **Commenting System** below each article
- ***Search Functionality***
    - Full-Text Search across Articles
    - Filter and Sort Results by Category
- *Multimedia Support*
    - Video and Image Embedding in Articles
- *Notifications*
    - Newsletter and sign up area from Newsletters
- ***Analytics and Reporting***
    - User Analytics Dashboard
    - Content Performance Metrics
    - SEO Optimization in all articles
- ***Security Features***
    - User Authentication and Authorization
    - Data Encryption (HTTPS)
- *User Management*
    - User Registration & Login
    - Profile Management
    - Password Recovery
    - saved aricles

- Personalized Content Recommendations

Not required as of now for sure.

Community Features*
- Forums and Discussion Boards

- Messaging Between Users
- Email and In-App Notifications for New Content
    - Push Notifications for Mobile Users